channel.title: Built a PC, need help now
channel.description:
I bought a bunch of shit from newegg, and was supprised when my first full build or w/e you wanna call it worked, but now i am sitting here with horrible graphics, if i install the driver from the website, which i think is the right one, i get 640-480 and 4bit color, if i use the cd that came with the mobo, when it reboots, there is no display at all, i am confused as hell, cansome one help me get this pc up and running nicely. Mobo: Biostar onboard video: Nvidia Geforce 8100 M2+ SE CPU: AMD 64 x2 dual core 5200+ 2.7ghz Memory: 2x1gig OCZ Reaper
lol, upgraded from a sstock dell inspironb130 with 1.6ghz and 512 megs of ram...
